title: Alcatel-Lucent Enterprise Application Fluent Networks
text: Compare Competitors Product Assessment - Data Center Switching Infrastructure ALE is evolving its networking product line with Intelligent Fabric, a new high-density data center switch, and demonstrating interoperability with NSX and other SDN protocols, but ALE still suffers from low brand awareness.
